            "body": "Hi [~okalinin], this is a interesting issue. According to the description, if I understand correctly, could we avoid multiple NM crash if we reduce the \"yarn.nodemanager.localizer.cache.cleanup.interval-ms\" and increasing \"yarn.nodemanager.localizer.cache.target-size-mb\"?",
